snippet.title: Global Farmer | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam in Early Access! 🌾🌻🚜🧑🏼‍🌾

➡️https://links.aerosoft.com/GlobalFarmer

Revealing Global Farmer,  the Top-Down Agriculture and Farming Strategy Game where the Real World is your Playground. 

Choose your plot anywhere on the planet, break ground, plant crops according to the seasons and local weather conditions, earn cash, purchase better equipment and expand your operations!

For more news and information join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/XPfvzjYE7A

Follow us also on our Aerosoft channels: 
Twitter
https://twitter.com/AerosoftGmbH
Instagram
https://www.instagram.com/aerosoft_gmbh
Facebook
https://www.facebook.com/Aerosoft

If you are a content creator and want to request a key or have any other inquiry, please contact us here:
marketing@aerosoft.de

#globalfarmer #farmsim #farmingsimulator
